.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
The \fBSoPerspectiveCamera\fP class defines a camera node with perspective rendering\&.
.PP
For realistic looking 3D scene, the geometry should be rendered with perspective calculations\&. Use this camera type to accomplish this\&. 

\fBFILE FORMAT/DEFAULTS:\fP 
.PP
.nf
PerspectiveCamera {
    viewportMapping ADJUST_CAMERA
    position 0 0 1
    orientation 0 0 1  0
    nearDistance 1
    farDistance 10
    aspectRatio 1
    focalDistance 5
    heightAngle 0\&.78539819
}

.fi
.PP
 
